				=09
					=09

<div class=3D"paragraph" style=3D"text-align:justify;">With the keyword in =
a matrix, we need to convert this into a key matrix. We do this by converti=
ng each letter into a number by its position in the alphabet (starting at 0=
). So, A =3D 0, B =3D 1, C=3D 2, D =3D 3, etc.<br></div>


